Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.89,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:19.06,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, I saw another shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:21.88,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You should make a wish next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.43,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,A wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:29.68,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yeah. A shooting star is the light that escapes whenever God opens the lid to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:35.29,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,If you make a wish when you see one, God will listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:39.21,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Really? I have a lot of wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:43.31,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I want to become a nurse and go to outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.62,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,There's no point in telling your Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.61,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You have to tell the star what your wish is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.04,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.74,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Um... Star-sama, Star-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.68,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Oh, I saw one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:30.05,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:36.84,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Turn it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:37.74,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:42.01,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, I apologize for the disturbance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.28,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Apologize to them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.25,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.78,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,You can finish this later. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:54.67,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:58.00,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Let us continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:02.67,DTB-Default,Scientist,0,0,0,,Upon analysis of the data obtained from the recording,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:08.62,DTB-Default,Scientist,0,0,0,,the location of the Lancernopt synchrotron radiation, believed to have been emitted by the meteor fragment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:12.11,DTB-Default,Scientist,0,0,0,,is definitely 3-17 Sotokanda, Chiyoda Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.33,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.85,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,You can see it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.85,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Don't act like you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:34.03,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I've seen people like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:38.95,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,People who lost their composure after being forced to see an illusion against their will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:43.28,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Please don't handle this by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.58,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,You can get it off your mind if you talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.00,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.71,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,That isn't part of your job, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:57.71,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,It'll be inconvenient for me if you go into a mental lapse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:06.30,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I realized my dreams when I came here, but I might be excused without being able to contribute any research.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.31,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.19,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,The syndicate won't dispose of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.98,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.82,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I don't think it's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:18.08,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,The syndicate doesn't expect anything out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:22.61,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave before somebody sees us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.55,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.29,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.08,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.48,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.44,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.53,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Just cleaning up, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.53,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why the sudden change?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:05.80,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,The synchrotron radiation confirmed during the search the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:10.28,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,was determined to have originated from a precious, gate-proprietary material.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:14.21,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I was appointed as a member of the retrieval team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:20.21,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,The area has been under strict restrictions ever since the accident occurred to the reconnaissance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.86,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I have no idea how it moved to its current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.55,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,By the way, you're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.06,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I was thinking about giving it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.02,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.56,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.64,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Great. That's one less thing for me to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:48.38,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,Attention, all members of the Building No. 18 reconnaissance team,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:51.47,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,please proceed to Gate Seven in Sector Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.69,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Duty calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:57.89,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, but can I ask you to clean this place later?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.08,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:03.32,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,If I return safely, let's gaze at the stars again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.44,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.85,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,May I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.88,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.74,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.07,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,No hard feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.99,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,It was your fault for giving her the cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.34,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.45,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,You don't have to act so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.18,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:02.13,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fax0.1\bord0\shad0\fs50\fscx85\fnSegoe Print\c&H000000&\pos(714,666)\frz14.762}The upturned shoes placed next to\NCorinna's body... your contract payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.17,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.87,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Did you obtain any information from Kikuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:19.25,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I remembered he was the first one to discover the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:23.21,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I'm doing what I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:26.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I told you not to act on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.51,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,He's not a threat, though. He's only...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:33.64,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,He isn't dangerous, but the person supervising him is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.54,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Didn't you realize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.27,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You're here because you wanted to realize your dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.50,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,If that's true, don't think about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.23,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:54.16,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I haven't done what you think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.74,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I only had a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:06.15,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,Emergency! Attention! All Building No. 18 analysis members, please return to your designated research areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.98,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,I repeat, this is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.46,DTB-Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.55,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:17.38,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,This is the feed we just received from the reconnaissance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:21.94,DTB-Default,Member,0,0,0,,Someone, send reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:26.30,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Chief, there's something strange about this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.08,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,The letters are backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:33.07,DTB-Default,Member,0,0,0,,I-I don't know what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.08,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Stop it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.00,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Rewind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.08,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Right there. Zoom in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.86,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,What is... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.60,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.49,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Twelve When One Takes Back What Was Lost Within the Wall... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.03,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,You're not going to conduct another search?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.63,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about the meteor fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.86,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Nick wasn't able to retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:30.53,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,As the supervisor of the team, I cannot afford to lose any more of our researchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.52,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.16,DTB-Default,Eric,0,0,0,,Did you retrieve the meteor fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.89,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.17,DTB-Default,Eric,0,0,0,,I'm sure you already know, but this is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:53.45,DTB-Default,Eric,0,0,0,,I can no longer persuade the chief executives, even with my level of influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.32,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Nick-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.97,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.92,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.90,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.28,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.33,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I've decided to quit this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.64,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,The chief has already negotiated with PANDORA headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.10,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What are you going to do after you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.92,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,It's earlier than I had anticipated, but I'm thinking about returning to NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:30.67,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,It's only one-fifth of its original size during its prime, but it still technically exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:34.59,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,The promise of gazing at the stars will have to wait until after I leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.20,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,When the time comes, please invite your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.33,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.42,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Ever since we first met, I never thought of you as a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:51.34,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,It felt like I was seeing a different part of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.32,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I'm glad we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.06,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Mina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:07.17,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why did you resort to such a conspicuous method?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.65,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.92,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Why was Nick the only one who made it back alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:17.88,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I checked all of the video tapes since that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.22,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,but he doesn't show up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.14,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Nick's absent in all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.85,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,In addition, everyone's shoes were turned over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.16,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,This incident wasn't caused by the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.11,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,It's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.00,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,his doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:33.90,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.95,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,How long have you two been working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.94,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Did you ever think he was a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.49,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.91,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,After meeting you, I'm not so sure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:53.92,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,You're nicer than the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:57.92,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,so I don't want you to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:03.74,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm acting this way or saying these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.52,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I never had any other interests aside from research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.47,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Ever since I met you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:20.78,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.76,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Is that where the meteor fragment is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:28.83,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Slowly move backwards and put your hands against the locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.43,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.01,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Li-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.77,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.38,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You witnessed what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.21,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,It's only natural to be suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.98,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,but I want you to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.74,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,This is the meteor fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:32.55,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I was hired by the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:38.71,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I was ordered to retrieve the material within the gate in exchange for a position in NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.65,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I'm not fond of the management here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:46.64,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Research data is sent to the upper divisions and never disclosed with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.66,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I don't even know what the other teams are researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.50,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll never realize my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:59.51,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I won't be able to retrieve the real sky or take my sister out to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.89,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,It sounds eccentric, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.78,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:10.49,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I wanted you to believe in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:16.72,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,A long time ago, I saw the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:26.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Contractors, who became so proficient that they were unable to control their abilities, started killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.54,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Everything you've said up to now was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:36.08,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,This won't bring the real starry sky back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.85,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,The dreams you talked about, your sister, everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:44.80,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,After all, contractors aren't able to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.78,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.30,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Why doesn't my ability have any effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.06,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,We even have the same abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.35,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You and I are nearly identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.58,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Contractors do not dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:12.10,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,True, I may have had those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.82,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,That's why I trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:19.19,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be able to understand my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.79,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,In the end, I was the one stupid enough to have trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.38,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Out of everyone, I didn't want to drag you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.17,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.33,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Li-kun, the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.85,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You believed in me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.76,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:26.94,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Yin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:54.02,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Go to Gate Eleven in Research Building Three, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.32,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Arrangements have been made for your departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.38,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You knew about everything, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.33,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You even knew Nick was the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.85,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Yes, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.02,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,In that case, why didn't you take care of him earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:15.45,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,I had to see it with my own eyes... the power of the meteor fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.41,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What's to become of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.39,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Her daily life won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.73,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,She found what she had lost and completed her remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.42,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.66,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Even Huang said you should rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:48.87,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:54.67,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Do you think the real starry sky will return someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:20:00.61,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You can only retrieve what you lost inside the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.26,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Then again, that's probably a rumor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.76,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Oh, it's that black cat again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.43,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.10,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Wait, you stupid cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.78,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:44.52,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The glow of the moon displays a distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.37,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,the warmth of youthful days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.33,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,That happy feeling in my memories is an intangible mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:58.23,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The melodies resonate against the dull, grey eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.80,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,but there is no soul to receive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.26,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Everything has disappeared with the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Thirteen A Heart Unswaying on the Water's Surface... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:08.60,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Your soul begins to wander.